guiPack

Class Edge

  • java.lang.Object
    • guiPack.Edge

  • public class Edge
extends java.lang.Object
    The Edge object represents an edge in graph theory between two nodes. More specifically between two MapNodes. The edge is weighted.
    Author:
    Douglas Wallin
